Requirement:
 to fetch the month based on integer. Without using if conditions and all. Like if the  integer is 1 I need to get January.
 
 Concept Covered: DataTime , Date, Concat, java import of Month


Solution 1:

%dw 2.0
output application/json
import java!java::time::Month

---
Month::of(1)



Solution : 2   -> Requires to pass additional hardcoded value

%dw 2.0
output application/json
var passMonthVal = "02"
var sampleDateYear = "-01-2020"
var concatText = passMonthVal ++ sampleDateYear
---
concatText as Date {format : "MM-dd-yyyy"} as String {format : "MMM"} 




